{"title":"Uri","link":"/en/wol/d/r1/lp-e/1200004520","html":"<span id=\"page1142\" class=\"pageNum\" data-no=\"1142\" data-before-text=\"1142\"></span><strong>URI</strong>(U&#x2B9;ri) [from a root meaning &#x201C;light&#x201D;].<strong>1. </strong>A descendant of Judah through Perez, Hezron, Caleb, and Hur. Uri&#x2019;s son Bezalel was a noted tabernacle craftsman.<wbr>&#x2014;<a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004520/0/0\" data-bid=\"1-1\" class=\"b\">Ex 31:2;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004520/0/1\" data-bid=\"1-2\" class=\"b\"> 35:30;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004520/0/2\" data-bid=\"1-3\" class=\"b\"> 38:22;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004520/0/3\" data-bid=\"1-4\" class=\"b\"> 1Ch 2:4, 5,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004520/0/4\" data-bid=\"1-5\" class=\"b\"> 9,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004520/0/5\" data-bid=\"1-6\" class=\"b\"> 18-20;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004520/0/6\" data-bid=\"1-7\" class=\"b\"> 2Ch 1:5</a>.<strong>2. </strong>Father of Geber, who was one of Solomon&#x2019;s food deputies.<wbr>&#x2014;<a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004520/1/0\" data-bid=\"2-1\" class=\"b\">1Ki 4:7,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004520/1/1\" data-bid=\"2-2\" class=\"b\">&#xA0;19</a>.<strong>3. </strong>One of the three Levite gatekeepers who sent away their foreign wives and sons as a result of Ezra&#x2019;s counsel.<wbr>&#x2014;<a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004520/2/0\" data-bid=\"3-1\" class=\"b\">Ezr 10:10, 11,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004520/2/1\" data-bid=\"3-2\" class=\"b\"> 24,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004520/2/2\" data-bid=\"3-3\" class=\"b\">&#xA0;44</a>."}